        "text": "In a more modern example, in August 2005, a patent pool was formed by about 20 companies active in the Radio Frequency Identification (RFID) ([[RFID]]) domain.[http://www.rfidjournal.com/article/articleview/1798/1/1/ The RFID Patent Pool: Next Steps]  The RFID Consortium picked Via Licensing to administer its patent pool in September 2006.[http://www.rfidjournal.com/article/articleview/2636/1/1/ RFID Consortium Names Patent-Pool Administrator]"
